	<li class="menu-item menu-item-type-custom menu-item-object-custom"><a href="https://dimesociety.org/ai-implementation-in-healthcare-playbook/"><span class="uk-margin-small-right" uk-icon="icon: home;"></span> The Playbook</a></li>
