<div class="uk-width-1-2@m">
    
        
            
            
            
                
                    
<div class="uk-h6">        SECTION 1 | IDENTIFY THE PROBLEM    </div>
                
            
        
    
</div></div><div class="uk-grid tm-grid-expand uk-child-width-1-1 uk-grid-margin uk-margin-remove-top">
<div class="uk-width-1-1">
    
        
            
            
            
                
                    
<h1 class="uk-heading-xlarge uk-text-secondary">        Health AI Readiness Assessment    </h1><div class="uk-panel uk-margin"><p><strong>Approximate time: 10 minutes</strong></p>
<p>This interactive self-assessment guides you through a structured review of your organization’s readiness to implement health AI across the seven domains of our <a href="https://dimesociety.org/ai-implementation-in-healthcare-playbook/ai-evaluation-readiness/health-ai-maturity-model/">Maturity Model</a>.</p></div>
<div class="uk-margin">
    
    
        
        
<a class="el-content uk-button uk-button-text uk-flex-inline uk-flex-center uk-flex-middle" href="#js-0" uk-toggle>
        <span class="uk-margin-small-right" uk-icon="info"></span>    
        INSTRUCTIONS    
    
</a>

<div id="js-0" uk-modal class="uk-modal">    <div class="uk-modal-dialog uk-margin-auto-vertical uk-modal-body">
        <button class="uk-modal-close-default" uk-close type="button"></button>
                <h3>Instructions</h3>
<p>Answer the questions <strong>based on your current, implemented practices</strong>.</p>
<p>Go through the exercise individually or with a cross-functional team of clinical, data, and IT leaders.</p>
<p>There are 4 questions for each of the 7 domains. Check all that apply.</p>
<hr />
<h3>Your responses will generate a personalized readiness report</h3>
<p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" src="https://fpdtac9mhctc-u4418.pressidiumcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/Screenshot-2025-09-04-at-8.52.45 PM-1024x744.png" alt="Personal Health AI Readiness Report" width="1024" class="alignnone wp-image-77431 size-large" height="744" srcset="https://fpdtac9mhctc-u4418.pressidiumcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/Screenshot-2025-09-04-at-8.52.45 PM-1024x744.png 1024w, https://fpdtac9mhctc-u4418.pressidiumcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/Screenshot-2025-09-04-at-8.52.45 PM-300x218.png 300w, https://fpdtac9mhctc-u4418.pressidiumcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/Screenshot-2025-09-04-at-8.52.45 PM-768x558.png 768w, https://fpdtac9mhctc-u4418.pressidiumcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/Screenshot-2025-09-04-at-8.52.45 PM-1536x1116.png 1536w, https://fpdtac9mhctc-u4418.pressidiumcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/Screenshot-2025-09-04-at-8.52.45 PM-600x436.png 600w, https://fpdtac9mhctc-u4418.pressidiumcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/Screenshot-2025-09-04-at-8.52.45 PM.png 1838w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p>Your report is designed to:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Evaluate</strong> your current-state maturity for each domain.</li>
<li><strong>Highlight</strong> your strengths and potential risk exposure.</li>
<li><strong>Deliver</strong> a targeted roadmap with the specific benchmarks you need to meet to advance to the next level.</li>
</ul>        
        </div></div>

        
    
    
</div>

                
            
        
    
</div></div>
